<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sol's RNG Assets</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Rajdhani:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #07080b;
            color: #f1f5f9;
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* Clean, high-fidelity HUD style using classic Sol's RNG dark interface colors */
        .hud-card {
            background-color: #0f1015;
            border: 1px solid #20222b;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* High-contrast solid corner brackets inspired by image_bbb5a3.png (completely flat, no glow) */
        .hud-corner {
            position: absolute;
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            border-color: #ffffff;
            border-style: solid;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .hud-corner-tl { top: -2px; left: -2px; border-width: 3px 0 0 3px; }
        .hud-corner-tr { top: -2px; right: -2px; border-width: 3px 3px 0 0; }
        .hud-corner-bl { bottom: -2px; left: -2px; border-width: 0 0 3px 3px; }
        .hud-corner-br { bottom: -2px; right: -2px; border-width: 0 3px 3px 0; }

        /* Custom scrollbar to match the high-contrast HUD */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: #0f1015;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: #3e4152;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: #5a5e75;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="p-4 md:p-12 relative flex items-center justify-center">

    <div class="max-w-4xl w-full mx-auto space-y-6 relative z-10">
        
        <!-- Header Panel -->
        <header class="hud-card p-6 text-center rounded-sm">
            <div class="hud-corner hud-corner-tl"></div>
            <div class="hud-corner hud-corner-tr"></div>
            <div class="hud-corner hud-corner-bl"></div>
            <div class="hud-corner hud-corner-br"></div>
            
            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[#ffbf00] font-bold mb-1">Asset Repository</p>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-wider text-white">
                SOL'S RNG ASSETS
            </h1>
            <div class="mt-3 flex items-center justify-center gap-4 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400">
                <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5 uppercase">
                    <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#10b981]"></span>
                    Status: Verified
                </span>
                <span class="text-slate-700">|</span>
                <span class="uppercase">Build: V0.1</span>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- Main Info Grid -->
        <main class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            
            <section class="hud-card p-6 flex flex-col justify-between rounded-sm">
                <div class="hud-corner hud-corner-tl"></div>
                <div class="hud-corner hud-corner-tr"></div>
                <div class="hud-corner hud-corner-bl"></div>
                <div class="hud-corner hud-corner-br"></div>
                
                <div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3 text-cyan-400 font-bold uppercase text-sm tracking-wider">
                        <span class="text-lg">▪</span> Disclaimer
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Original Assets</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 text-base leading-relaxed font-medium">
                        Everything I created is literally made by me, including all of the interfaces.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-6 pt-3 border-t border-slate-800 text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">
                    Source Verified // 100% Custom Work
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="hud-card p-6 flex flex-col justify-between rounded-sm">
                <div class="hud-corner hud-corner-tl"></div>
                <div class="hud-corner hud-corner-tr"></div>
                <div class="hud-corner hud-corner-bl"></div>
                <div class="hud-corner hud-corner-br"></div>
                
                <div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3 text-red-400 font-bold uppercase text-sm tracking-wider">
                        <span class="text-lg">▪</span> Recommendation
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Copyright Notice</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-300 text-base leading-relaxed font-medium">
                        If you are going to make an RNG game, I would not recommend using these Interfaces, Sounds, and Auras. If a Sol's RNG DEV sees your game, they might take it down due to copyright infringement (it is not the first time this has happened).
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-6 pt-3 border-t border-slate-800 text-xs text-red-400/80 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">
                    Alert for External Creators
                </div>
            </section>

        </main>

        <section class="hud-card p-6 rounded-sm">
            <div class="hud-corner hud-corner-tl"></div>
            <div class="hud-corner hud-corner-tr"></div>
            <div class="hud-corner hud-corner-bl"></div>
            <div class="hud-corner hud-corner-br"></div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4 text-[#bf7afb] font-bold uppercase text-sm tracking-wider">
                <span class="text-lg">▪</span> Current Release Highlights
            </div>
            
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Update V0.1</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-300 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6 font-medium">
                This release features a fully functional equip/skip aura loop alongside the following standard deployment systems: Roll, Autoroll, and Quick roll.
            </p>
            
            <div class="overflow-x-auto border border-slate-800 rounded-sm">
                <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse text-sm">
                    <thead>
                        <tr class="bg-white/[0.03] border-b border-slate-800 text-slate-300 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-bold">
                            <th class="p-3.5 border-r border-slate-800">System Name</th>
                            <th class="p-3.5">Behavior & Description</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-800/80">
                        <tr class="hover:bg-white/[0.01] transition-colors">
                            <td class="p-3.5 font-bold text-cyan-400 whitespace-nowrap border-r border-slate-800 uppercase tracking-wide">Roll System</td>
                            <td class="p-3.5 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                                Pressing the Roll button triggers a short animation of approximately 2.5s or 3.2s. Once the animation finishes, your rolled aura is displayed with clean options to either equip or skip the result.
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="hover:bg-white/[0.01] transition-colors">
                            <td class="p-3.5 font-bold text-cyan-400 whitespace-nowrap border-r border-slate-800 uppercase tracking-wide">Autoroll System</td>
                            <td class="p-3.5 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                                Keeps rolling continuously and automatically for your account without requiring manual input.
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr class="hover:bg-white/[0.01] transition-colors">
                            <td class="p-3.5 font-bold text-cyan-400 whitespace-nowrap border-r border-slate-800 uppercase tracking-wide">Quick Roll System</td>
                            <td class="p-3.5 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                                Bypasses all visual effects and roll animations to render results instantly for accelerated testing.
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer class="text-center text-xs text-slate-500 tracking-widest uppercase pt-4 font-semibold">
            System Authorized // Sol's RNG Unofficial News & Assets Feed
        </footer>

    </div>

</body>
</html>
